information: We have been exporting Holstein-Friesian, Simmental and Fleckvieh dairy cattle for 32 years. We also export Braunvieh and Jersey cattle, as well as East-Friesian, Lacaune and Awassi dairy sheep, and sheep reared for meat including Merino, Suffolk, Berrichon, Ile de France and Texel sheep. We also offer a wide range of pregnant and calving cows available to buy both on the farm and at auction, including Holsteiner Schwarzbunte cattle as well as Simmental-Fleckvieh and Braunvieh cattle.
